snippet.title: Cult of The Wind Review  - Worth a Buy?
snippet.description:
Cult of the Wind is a game about people who pretend to be airplanes.  But is it Worth a Buy?  Mack thinks it would be more fun to talk about the failing school education system.

Please note at the time this video was produced the game cost £10.99 it is now reduced to £6.99
